41#ifndef _DEVICE_H
42#define _DEVICE_H
43
44#include "iscsiprotocol.h"
45#include "target.h"
46
47/*
48 * Interface from target to device:
49 *
50 * device_init() initializes the device
51 * device_command() sends a SCSI command to one of the logical units in the device.
52 * device_shutdown() shuts down the device.
53 */
54
55int device_init(iscsi_target_t *, targv_t *, disc_target_t *);
56int device_command(target_session_t *, target_cmd_t *);
57int device_shutdown(target_session_t *);
58void device_set_var(const char *, const char *);
59
60#endif /* _DEVICE_H */
